title: India's Kumar opens 'floodgates to a billion' people with historic darts win
subtitle: Nitin Kumar becomes first Indian player to win a match at the World Darts Championship with a 3-2 win over Dutchman Richard Veenstra 3-2.
full_text: Nitin Kumar becomes first Indian player to win a match at the World Darts Championship with a 3-2 win over Dutchman Richard Veenstra 3-2.
